  "title": "Improving GitLab's deletion flow: What to expect in coming months",
  "link": "https://about.gitlab.com/blog/improving-gitlab-deletion-flow-what-to-expect-in-coming-months/",
  "description": "",
  "author": "Christina Lohr",
